eveloper session for bootstrap-backup. Follow current SOUL/AGENTS rules, including OpenSpec-first for significant work.\n\nRequired approach:\n1. Check whether this UI scaling change is best implemented via root typography/base layout/container scale tokens, not one-off page hacks.\n2. Because project has OpenSpec available, create or align to minimal OpenSpec change/spec context first if none exists yet.\n3. Then implement the FE change.\n4. Prefer system-wide, maintainable adjustment over per-page patching.\n5. Avoid breaking responsive behavior.\n6. Verify by running the FE and checking the affected root layout/theme/global CSS files.\n7. Write/update handover with exact files changed and short rationale.\n\nExpected output back to Orbis:\n- diagnosis of root cause\n- implementation approach chosen\n- exact files changed\n- whether change is global or partial\n- any risks / follow-up QA notes\n\nDo the work now.","model":"sonnet","thinking":"medium","timeoutSeconds":1800},"delivery":{"mode":"announce"},"state":{"lastRunAtMs":1775880052010,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":280751,"lastError":"Delivering to Telegram requires target <chatId>","lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":1}},{"id":"43dc76cd-a867-4619-b773-3f6e59ebb6f7","agentId":"team-orchestrator","sessionKey":"agent:team-orchestrator:main","name":"ahv-driving-backend-qa-audit-now","enabled":false,"deleteAfterRun":true,"createdAtMs":1775865358843,"updatedAtMs":1775866022055,"schedule":{"kind":"at","at":"2026-04-10T23:56:30.000Z"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Project root: /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend\n\nYou are QA Reviewer. Do not implement code. Audit backend quality/risk only.\n\nScope:\n- Review request flow, error flow, auth middleware usage, validation coverage, logging consistency, env/config hygiene, and obvious performance/code-quality risks.\n- Review key modu