{"type":"message","id":"ce1a4e85","parentId":"4f6c8592","timestamp":"2026-04-12T13:41:06.881Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me compile the agent status:\n\n**Active Sessions (17 total):**\n1. `master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134` — running ✅ (main direct session with Khuowgn)\n2. `master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef` — running ✅ (cron 5p DTLX)\n3. `master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d` — running ✅ (cron 5p AHV Works)\n4. `master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492` — done (DTLX group session)\n\n\n5. `master-orchestrator:main` — done (heartbeat)\n6. `master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258` — done (stale group session)\n7. `prompt-optimizer:telegram:group:-5168104492` — done\n8. `prompt-optimizer:subagent:0eb3c914` — failed ❌\n9. `prompt-optimizer:telegram:slash:6053576134` — no messages\n10. `master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728` — done (AHV Works group)\n11. `security-reviewer:subagent:6739034d` — done\n12. `performance-optimizer:subagent:57b179b5` — done (but had errors with AHV-Holding-TroLy model)\n13. `senior-backend:subagent:31b6b412` — done\n14. `senior-frontend:subagent:fd28add5` — done\n15. `database-reviewer:subagent:51a096dc` — done (had error with AHV-Holding-TroLy model)\n16. `code-reviewer:subagent:370ec3dd` — failed ❌\n17. `master-orchestrator:telegram:slash:6053576134` — no messages\n\nThe system shows 17 sessions total with mostly completed tasks, though there are a couple of failures from the subagents and some errors related to the model configuration.\n\nLooking at what's currently active, I've got 3 sessions running right now: the main orchestration session with Khuowgn and two background cron jobs handling periodic updates for both DTLX and AHV Works. The rest are either completed or stale. There's also an outdated group session at -5163901258 that should be cleaned up, plus a few other sessions that need attention.\n\nThe main issues I'm seeing are a couple of failed subagents—the prompt-optimizer had an MCP failure around 11:11 UTC and the code-reviewer session failed, though it was actually mid-analysis when it crashed. The performance and database reviewer sessions ran into model compatibility problems, using an older TroLy model that doesn't work well with the tools. On top of that, there's that old group session lingering that should be removed.\n\nThe AHV Works review cycle did complete successfully, with the backend, frontend, and security reviews all finishing their reports in the group session, even though the subagents themselves had some issues.","thinkingSignature":"96feae4148c95deb8dfdcdb604360a50f9391d9579e8dd6fb7941f15209d8ea3"},{"type":"text","text":"Dưới đây là tổng quan toàn hệ thống:\n\n---\n\n## 🌐 Orbis — Agent Status Report | 13:38 UTC 12 Apr\n\n### ✅ Active Sessions (3)\n\n| Session | Trạng thái | Ghi chú |\n|---|---|---|\n| `master-orchestrator` direct (Khuowgn) | 🟡 Running | Đang tương tác |\n| `cron: 5p Progress Report — AHV DTLX` | 🟢 Running | Theo dõi group -5168104492 |\n| `cron: 5p Progress Report — AHV Works` | 🟢 Running | Theo dõi group -5212380728 |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Done (historical — KHÔNG còn chạy)\n\n| Session | Kết quả |\n|---|---|\n| `group:-5212380728` (AHV Works review) | ✅ Đã hoàn thành — review BE/FE/Security |\n| `group:-5168104492` (DTLX status) | ✅ Đã hoàn thành — báo cáo DTLX/QLHV |\n| `security-reviewer:subagent` | ✅ Done — 6 critical vulns found |\n| `senior-frontend:subagent` | ✅ Done — Checkins broken, any types everywhere |\n| `senior-backend:subagent` | ✅ Done |\n| `prompt-optimizer:group` | ✅ Done — đã optimize prompt |\n\n---\n\n### ❌ Failed / Error (cần lưu ý)\n\n| Session | Lỗi | Nguyên nhân |\n|---|---|---|\n| `code-reviewer:subagent:370ec3dd` | ❌ Failed | Bị crash giữa chừng (đang phân tích code → dở) |\n| `prompt-optimizer:subagent:0eb3c914` | ❌ Failed | MCP error gọi bot |\n\n### ⚠️ Model Error (chạy được nhưng model yếu)\n\n| Session | Vấn đề |\n|---|---|\n| `performance-optimizer:subagent` | Dùng `AHV-Holding-TroLy` → 2 lỗi `providerSpecificData` |\n| `database-reviewer:subagent` | Dùng `AHV-Holding-TroLy` → lỗi tương tự |\n\n---\n\n### 🗑️ Stale Sessions (nên xóa)\n\n| Session | Ghi chú |\n|---|---|\n| `telegram:group:-5163901258` | Group ID cũ — không tồn tại |\n\n---\n\n### 📊 Tóm tắt\n\n```\nPipeline:  🟡 DEGRADED (nhẹ)\n• Active:  3 sessions (1 direct + 2 cron)\n• Failed:  2 subagents (code-reviewer, prompt-optimizer sub)\n• Model:   2 agent dùng TroLy yếu — cần set lại model\n\nMCP:       ✅ stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab\nCron:      ✅ 5p DTLX ✅ 5p Works ✅ Daily 5AM\n```\n\n**Cần can thiệp:**\n1. Re-run `code-reviewer` — nó crash giữa chừng, chưa viết được báo cáo\n2. Sửa model cho `performance-optimizer` + `database-reviewer` → đổi sang `AHV-Holding-DEV`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":18320,"output":1425,"cacheRead":33134,"cacheWrite":367,"totalTokens":53246,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776001238342,"responseId":"062ad3d767a4ea61704b8e44f753745f"}}
