y anyone, no machine key enforced\\n2. **IDOR in `/niko-wallets/:id`** — any user's wallet balance readable by any authenticated user\\n3. **IDOR in `/employees/:id`** — `verifyAdminOrOwner` not applied to the route\\n4. **IDOR in `/leave-requests/:id`** — leave data readable without ownership check\\n5. **Hardcoded department bypass** — users in a specific department code get silent admin access (`author.middleware.ts`)\\n6. **Swagger `/docs` unauthenticated** — full API surface exposed to anyone\\n\\n**5 High risks** including missing rate limiting on login, default `123456` password fallback, refresh token cookie always `secure: false`, and inconsistent token version checking in the auth flow.\\n\\n**9 Medium risks** covering missing Helmet headers, regex injection via unsanitized query params, missing manager checks on leave approvals, permissive CORS defaults, and no audit logging for sensitive operations.\\n\\n**Priority fix list** with 16 items ranked P1→P4 with estimated fix times included for the dev team.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 109,\n            \"output\": 306,\n            \"totalTokens\": 56554,\n            \"cacheRead\": 48784,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 7355,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1775982210718,\n          \"responseId\": \"062a89841dc420b8807b887134a52249\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"5399cca6\",\n            \"seq\": 91\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:slash:6053576134\",\n      \"kind\": \"group\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayNa