{"type":"message","id":"f08449b5","parentId":"874256da","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:32:11.934Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hdztup5ve772_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31\",\n      \"agentId\": \"master-orchestrator\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"name\": \"5p Progress Report — AHV DTLX\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775986516041,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1776051614938,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 300000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1775986440000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV DTLX (Đào Tạo Lái Xe) ecosystem.\\n\\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\\n\\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\\n\\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, task started/completed, blocker appeared), compose a concise change report to group -5168104492:\\n\\nFormat:\\n🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\\n\\nChanges detected:\\n• [list of actual changes]\\n\\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\\n• Active sessions: N\\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\n\\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"-5168104492\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1776055214938,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1776051494048,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 120890,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 5,\n        \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\",\n        \"lastError\": \"cron: job execution timed out\"\n      },\n      \"description\": \"5-minute change detection for AHV DTLX + QLHV group -5168104492. Only reports when sessions change/fail.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\",\n      \"agentId\": \"master-orchestrator\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"name\": \"5p Progress Report — AHV Works\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775975347574,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1776054466020,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 300000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1775975347574\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV Works ecosystem.\\n\\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\\n\\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\\n\\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, blocker appeared, task completed), compose a concise change report to group -5212380728:\\n\\nFormat:\\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\\n\\nChanges detected:\\n• [list of actual changes]\\n\\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\\n• Active sessions: N\\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\\n• Blockers: none / [list blockers]\\n\\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n    