":20551,"output_tokens":326,"total_tokens":34208},"delivered":true,"deliveryStatus":"delivered","sessionId":"4b588744-e6bd-4b2c-92a8-6d9d577ad7a0","sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31:run:4b588744-e6bd-4b2c-92a8-6d9d577ad7a0"},{"ts":1776024530089,"jobId":"6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"**Silent exit — no state change detected.**\n\nComparing current snapshot (20:08 UTC) against prior stable baseline (19:23 UTC):\n\n- ✅ Same 2 cron sessions running (`cron:ed2d0b5d`, `cron:6f3323ef`)\n- ✅ Same 17 historical sessions (15 done, 4 failed — all from prior review runs)\n- ✅ No new spawns, no deaths, no completions, no blockers\n\nPipeline: **STABLE**. Silent exit.","runAtMs":1776024494292,"durationMs":35784,"nextRunAtMs":1776024794292,"model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","provider":"ahvholding","usage":{"input_tokens":29485,"output_tokens":565,"total_tokens":43148},"delivered":true,"deliveryStatus":"delivered","sessionId":"300f8972-e66a-421a-bc75-a7a12bb83940","sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31:run:300f8972-e66a-421a-bc75-a7a12bb83940"}],"total":130,"offset":0,"limit":50,"hasMore":true,"nextOffset":50},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776055225967}}
{"type":"message","id":"ed7485da","parentId":"5daf6307","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:40:46.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great news! The cron runs show that the DTLX cron is actually working again! Looking at the most recent runs:\n\n1. **04:34 UTC** - `status: ok` ✅ - Delivered to group -5168104492\n2. **04:32 UTC** - `status: ok` ✅ - Delivered to group -5168104492\n\nThe cron is back! The timeout issue was fixed when I increased it to 300s. The latest run at 04:34 was successful.\n\nHowever, Lead is asking specifically about the group `-5168104492` not working. The cron IS delivering to that group now. But Lead might mean that the master-orchestrator isn't responding to messages in that group. \n \nI'm seeing multiple sessions for this group—one from April 12 that's still running with active subagents handling a settings page rebuild and FE refactoring. There's also a separate Telegram session for the same group, but the status is unclear since the session list timed out. The cron is working and delivering reports, but I need to figure out what specifically isn't functioning for the group itself. which is `-5163901258` according to the session. The cron DTLX reports to `-5168104492` (the QLHV group) but there's actually a different session for the DTLX ecosystem group at `-5163901258`.\n\nWait, I had updated MEMORY.md to say DTLX group is `-5168104492`. But there's also a separate session `agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258` which is labeled as `telegram:g-ahv-dtlx-ecosystem`. This is confusing.\n\nThe cron job for DTLX (6f3323ef) is delivering to `-5168104492` (QLHV group), but there's a separate group session with the old DTLX ID `-5163901258` that's still active and running subagents.\n\nI need to clarify which group the Lead is actually referring to, since `-5168104492` appears to be the QLHV group based on its label, while `-5163901258` seems to be the actual DTLX ecosystem group where work is happening.","thinkingSignature":"e63b06d79e36788fc71f1d38ecdaa4261a4e348fa67cb54723b7d378c73a2ae0"},{"type":"text","text":"Tin tốt Lead! **Cron DTLX đã hoạt động lại** ✅\n\nVừa thấy trong run history:\n- `04:34 UTC` → ✅ Delivered to `-5168104492` \n- `04:32 UTC` → ✅ Delivered to `-5168104492`\n\nĐã tăng timeout lên 300s và cron tự phục hồi sau gateway restart.\n\nNhưng để chắc chắn, cho Orbis biết: Lead gửi message vào group nào mà không thấy trả lời?\n- `-5168104492` (QLHV ecosystem) — cron đang gửi báo cáo vào đây ✅\n- `-5163901258` (DTLX ecosystem) — session đang chạy riêng cho DTLX"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":13859,"output":659,"cacheRead":90644,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105162,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776055226293,"responseId":"062ba6bc9400dc759a56c88502de5af6"}}
