{"type":"message","id":"eb03486e","parentId":"d1353d08","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:50:30.613Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gyqd84u6d2kk_1","toolName":"sessions_list","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"count\": 22,\n  \"sessions\": [\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:6053576134\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776055821034,\n      \"sessionId\": \"7ae3b683-0b91-4427-abbe-b78ef94eb140\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 104503,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776055820720,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"telegram:6053576134\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"main_bot\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/7ae3b683-0b91-4427-abbe-b78ef94eb140.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Great news! The cron runs show that the DTLX cron is actually working again! Looking at the most recent runs:\\n\\n1. **04:34 UTC** - `status: ok` ✅ - Delivered to group -5168104492\\n2. **04:32 UTC** - `status: ok` ✅ - Delivered to group -5168104492\\n\\nThe cron is back! The timeout issue was fixed when I increased it to 300s. The latest run at 04:34 was successful.\\n\\nHowever, Lead is asking specifically about the group `-5168104492` not working. The cron IS delivering to that group now. But Lead might mean that the master-orchestrator isn't responding to messages in that group. \\n \\nI'm seeing multiple sessions for this group—one from April 12 that's still running with active subagents handling a settings page rebuild and FE refactoring. There's also a separate Telegram session for the same group, but the status is unclear since the session list timed out. The cron is working and delivering reports, but I need to figure out what specifically isn't functioning for the group itself. which is `-5163901258` according to the session. The cron DTLX reports to `-5168104492` (the QLHV group) but there's actually a different session for the DTLX ecosystem group at `-5163901258`.\\n\\nWait, I had updated MEMORY.md to say DTLX group is `-5168104492`. But there's also a separate session `agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258` which is labeled as `telegram:g-ahv-dtlx-ecosystem`. This is confusing.\\n\\nThe cron job for DTLX (6f3323ef) is delivering to `-5168104492` (QLHV group), but there's a separate group session with the old DTLX ID `-5163901258` that's still active and running subagents.\\n\\nI need to clarify which group the Lead is actually referring to, since `-5168104492` appears to be the QLHV group based on its label, while `-5163901258` seems to be the actual DTLX ecosystem group where work is happening.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Tin tốt Lead! **Cron DTLX đã hoạt động lại** ✅\\n\\nVừa thấy trong run history:\\n- `04:34 UTC` → ✅ Delivered to `-5168104492` \\n- `04:32 UTC` → ✅ Delivered to `-5168104492`\\n\\nĐã tăng timeout lên 300s và cron tự phục hồi sau gateway restart.\\n\\nNhưng để chắc chắn, cho Orbis biết: Lead gửi message vào group nào mà không thấy trả lời?\\n- `-5168104492` (QLHV ecosystem) — cron đang gửi báo cáo vào đây ✅\\n- `-5163901258` (DTLX ecosystem) — session đang chạy riêng cho DTLX\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 13859,\n            \"output\": 659,\n            \"totalTokens\": 105162,\n            \"cacheRead\": 90644,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776055226293,\n          \"responseId\": \"062ba6bc9400dc759a56c88502de5af6\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"ed7485da\",\n            \"seq\": 94\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"-5163901258 master của chat group này đang làm việc không sao tôi chưa thấy phản hồi\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776055820720,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"0b90b160\",\n            \"seq\": 95\n          },\n          \"senderLabel\": \"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Lead is asking about the master orchestrator for group -5163901258. Let me check the sessions for this group.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_gyqd84u6d2kk_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"messageLimit\": 3\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 0,\n            \"output\": 53,\n            \"totalTokens\": 104869,\n            \"cacheRead\": 10548,\n  