    }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 155,\n            \"output\": 99,\n            \"totalTokens\": 22436,\n            \"cacheRead\": 18520,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 3662,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776055813220,\n          \"responseId\": \"062ba905883c5685971062da842e3c37\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"93c69a36\",\n            \"seq\": 10\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492\",\n      \"kind\": \"group\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-ahv-dtlx-ecosystem\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:-5168104492\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776055241791,\n      \"sessionId\": \"b90d0cbf-72bc-4ccf-b0a9-5bf84f42e416\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 74465,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776055231264,\n      \"endedAt\": 1776055240469,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 9205,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:prompt-optimizer:subagent:0eb3c914-87cc-4bdd-9ee9-20aa3e6473e1\",\n        \"agent:senior-backend:subagent:ce81d04d-cc26-4b7d-82f4-704a8256c73b\",\n        \"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:05e6701d-36aa-491c-ab9d-8edd7eeb37f8\"\n      ],\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"telegram:-5168104492\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"main_bot\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/b90d0cbf-72bc-4ccf-b0a9-5bf84f42e416.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Now I have a full picture of the DTLX project. Let me compile the status report.\\n\\n**DTLX Backend (Project ID: 77055841):**\\n- Local: branch `feature/clean-architecture-migration`, commit `47d53ae` (Mar 30)\\n- Active branches: `develop`, `feature/clean-architecture-migration`, `refactor/main`, `production`, `main`, etc.\\n- **MR !166**: `feature/clean-architecture-migration` → `refactor/main` — status `can_be_merged`, no conflicts\\n- **Other unmerged branches**:\\n  - `fix/build-operability-and-typos` \\n  - `fix/conflict-production-v1.1.0` (already merged)\\n  - `hotfix/import-student`\\n  - `hotfix/unicode-normalization-nfc`\\n  - `optimization/conventions`\\n  - `refactor/antigravity`\\n  - `refactor/merge-api-common`\\n  - `refactor/split-app-server`\\n- **Merged**: `feature/api-refactor`, `feature/docs-api`, `fix/add-student-to-course`, `hotfix/docker`, `refactor/code-cleanup-phase-2`\\n\\n**DTLX Frontend (Project ID: 77055851):**\\n- No local clone\\n- No opened MRs\\n- Last activity: Apr 7\\n\\nThe main priority is merging MR !166 for the backend refactor, while the frontend needs to be set up locally and doesn't have any active merge requests.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"## 📊 DTLX — Project Track\\n\\n---\\n\\n### 🖥️ DTLX Backend (`ahv-dtlx-backend`) — Project ID: 77055841\\n\\n| Trạng thái | Chi tiết |\\n|---|---|\\n| **Local branch** | `feature/clean-architecture-migration` |\\n| **Last commit** | `47d53ae` — chore: course student repository! (Mar 30) |\\n| **Local sync** | ⚠️ Local behind `develop` by ~1 month |\\n\\n**MRs mở:**\\n\\n| MR | Source → Target | Trạng thái | Li