 Can merge, no conflicts | [🔗](https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend/-/merge_requests/166) |\n\n**Branches chưa merge (unmerged):**\n- `fix/build-operability-and-typos`\n- `hotfix/import-student`\n- `hotfix/unicode-normalization-nfc` — NFC unicode normalization fix\n- `optimization/conventions`\n- `refactor/antigravity`\n- `refactor/merge-api-common`\n- `refactor/split-app-server`\n\n---\n\n### 🖥️ DTLX Frontend (`ahv-dtlx-frontend`) — Project ID: 77055851\n\n| Trạng thái | Chi tiết |\n|---|---|\n| **Local** | ❌ Chưa clone |\n| **MRs mở** | Không có |\n| **Last activity** | Apr 7, 2026 (stale ~6 days) |\n\n---\n\n### 📋 Action Items\n\n| # | Task | Ưu tiên |\n|---|---|---|\n| 1 | Merge MR **!166** (clean-architecture → refactor/main) | 🔴 Cao |\n| 2 | Clone & setup DTLX FE local | 🔴 Cao |\n| 3 | Sync BE `develop` vs local `feature/clean-architecture-migration` | 🟡 Trung |\n| 4 | Review unmerged branches | 🟡 Trung |\n\nLead muốn Orbis xử lý bước nào?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":8213,"output":816,"totalTokens":74848,"cacheRead":62486,"cacheWrite":3333,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776055181338,"responseId":"062ba68f0d223c65002d2a273a3647f7","__openclaw":{"id":"28206b5c","seq":149}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@thuowgn_bot"}],"timestamp":1776055231263,"__openclaw":{"id":"537ddfe6","seq":150},"senderLabel":"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)"},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead mentioned Orbis again. This is likely a follow-up to the previous question about DTLX tracking. Orbis should ask what they want to do next."},{"type":"text","text":"Dạ Orbis đang online 🌐\n\nBạn muốn Orbis xử lý bước nào cho DTLX?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":70,"totalTokens":74535,"cacheRead":65330,"cacheWrite":9135,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776055231702,