{"type":"message","id":"a9223293","parentId":"a82d279e","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:54:43.406Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1887\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"sender\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 04:54 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)\",\n  \"id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"name\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"username\": \"khuowgn\"\n}\n```\n\nbạn cũng cần phải gửi báo cáo định kỳ cho tôi thông tin là có những agent master nào đang chạy tình trạng khoẻ không, đang làm task gì"}],"timestamp":1776056083313}}
{"type":"message","id":"b2f344fb","parentId":"a9223293","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:55:01.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead wants Orbis to also send periodic status reports about which master agents are running and what they're working on. Currently the cron jobs send change-based reports, but Lead wants proactive status reports about all active master sessions.\n\nLet me think about what to do:\n1. The current 5p cron jobs send change-based reports\n2. Lead wants proactive status about which agents are running and their tasks\n3. I should create a new cron job or modify existing ones to also send this info\n\nLet me create a new cron job that sends a periodic status of all active master sessions to the direct chat with Lead. Or maybe I should modify the existing crons to also include this info.\n\nActually, the simplest approach would be to add a new \"Master Status\" report that goes to Lead's direct chat, summarizing all active sessions and what they're doing.\n\n\nI'll set up a new cron job that runs every 10 minutes to give Lead a direct status update about all active sessions, since the group-specific cron jobs are already functioning well.","thinkingSignature":"313f2c7472187c6497175d1bfdfe36514174fe1d2be7b94a61347ccff5fedf45"},{"type":"text","text":"Hiểu rồi Lead. Để tôi tạo thêm cron report gửi trực tiếp cho Lead về tình trạng các agent đang chạy:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ngx7e1ur3lec_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"Agent Status to Lead","schedule":{"kind":"every","everyMs":600000,"anchorMs":1776056040000},"sessionTarget":"isolated","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"You are Orbis. Check sessions_list and compile a brief status of all ACTIVE master-orchestrator sessions (excluding this cron session).\n\nFor each active session, report:\n- Session key (shortened)\n- Status (running/done)\n- What it's doing (from context)\n- How long it's been running\n\nSend the report to Lead directly via sessions_send to sessionKey: agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\n\nFormat:\n🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nActive sessions: N\n• [session name]: [status] — [task/description] — [duration]\n\nIf only this cron session is active (no other sessions), send HEARTBEAT_OK only.\nIf there are no sessions at all, stay SILENT.","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"agentId":"master-orchestrator"}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":61,"output":556,"cacheRead":104706,"cacheWrite":12291,"totalTokens":117614,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776056083407,"responseId":"062baa15acd63d296d2f4aa23b224089"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4dc6ea5d","parentId":"b2f344fb","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:55:02.389Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ngx7e1ur3lec_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e\",\n  \"agentId\": \"master-orchestrator\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n  \"name\": \"Agent Status to Lead\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1776056102269,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1776056102269,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"every\",\n    \"everyMs\": 600000,\n    \"anchorMs\": 1776056040000\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"You are Orbis. Check sessions_list and compile a brief status of all ACTIVE master-orchestrator sessions (excluding this cron session).\\n\\nFor each active session, report:\\n- Session key (shortened)\\n- Status (running/done)\\n- What it's doing (from context)\\n- How long it's been running\\n\\nSend the report to Lead directly via sessions_send to sessionKey: agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\\n\\nFormat:\\n🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\\n\\nActive sessions: N\\n• [session name]: [status] — [task/description] — [duration]\\n\\nIf only this cron session is active (no other sessions), send HEARTBEAT_OK only.\\nIf there are no sessions at all, stay SILENT.\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"none\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1776056640000\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","agentId":"master-orchestrator","sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","name":"Agent Status to Lead","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1776056102269,"updatedAtMs":1776056102269,"schedule":{"kind":"every","everyMs":600000,"anchorMs":1776056040000},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"You are Orbis. Check sessions_list and compile a brief status of all ACTIVE master-orchestrator sessions (excluding this cron session).\n\nFor each active session, report:\n- Session key (shortened)\n- Status (running/done)\n- What it's doing (from context)\n- How long it's been running\n\nSend the report to Lead directly via sessions_send to sessionKey: agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\n\nFormat:\n🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nActive sessions: N\n• [session name]: [status] — [task/description] — [duration]\n\nIf only this cron session is active (no other sessions), send HEARTBEAT_OK only.\nIf there are no sessions at all, stay SILENT.","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1776056640000}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776056102295}}
{"type":"message","id":"e8576310","parentId":"4dc6ea5d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:55:11.665Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, the issue is that this cron sends to a direct session using sessions_send, but the delivery is \"none\" so it won't auto-deliver. Let me also think about whether this approach is right.\n\nActually, the better approach would be to deliver directly to the Lead's Telegram chat. But the cron job is an isolated session, and it can't easily send to the direct Telegram chat without using sessions_send.\n\nLet me think about this more carefully:\n1. The cron runs in isolated session\n2. It checks sessions_list\n3. It needs to send the report to Lead directly\n\nThe issue is that the `delivery` with `announce` to the direct chat might work if I set the right `to` parameter. But since the cron session is isolated, I need to use sessions_send to the direct session, OR I can set delivery to announce to the direct chat.\n\n\nI realize I can't use `delivery` for this since it's tied to the cron session itself, not the direct session. So I should either trigger the cron immediately to test it, or adjust the delivery target to send directly to Lead's Telegram chat instead.","thinkingSignature":"d3b78c0d8095754771b30a7c83b9898637c9197a417935c2a7af86a7d8f70def"},{"type":"text","text":"Cron mới đã tạo. Test ngay xem nó gửi được không:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kykla6s308d2_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"run","jobId":"e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":519,"output":306,"cacheRead":116503,"cacheWrite":1006,"totalTokens":118334,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776056102394,"responseId":"062baa278238c76adf82f54dff8003d0"}}
