{"type":"message","id":"c2b70aac","parentId":"be88a76d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:55:41.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron has been triggered. Let me wait a bit and check the result.\n\nActually, I should also update the HEARTBEAT.md to document this new cron job. And I should report to Lead about what I've done.\n\nLet me also update the delivery to use announce mode to the direct chat. The issue is that `announce` sends from the isolated session's channel, not from the cron owner. Let me check the cron result first.\n\nActually, the cron job I created uses `sessions_send` inside the agent turn to send to the direct session. This should work. Let me give it a minute and report to Lead.","thinkingSignature":"a650eb618dede989541ef7ee913f61c565020867c6bd1962d108c76f9bfb5ed9"},{"type":"text","text":"Đã trigger test. Chờ kết quả 1 phút...\n\nTrong lúc đó, tóm tắt cho Lead:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l2993wg4pmkw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sleep 60 && echo \"done\"","yieldMs":65000,"background":true}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":169,"output":216,"cacheRead":116948,"cacheWrite":1281,"totalTokens":118614,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776056112315,"responseId":"062baa3111c11b82f5b818aa501dc60a"}}
