{"type":"message","id":"66845806","parentId":"40f52100","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:55:49.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me wait for the result. While waiting, let me update the HEARTBEAT.md to document this new cron.","thinkingSignature":"7e23f562829c40c7bf713d84fb2ee36652ec1977a3386c04a36748927ea4a790"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xhf8qj8vpws1_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## 🚨 Always Report Immediately (no silence)\n\n| Condition | Action |\n|---|---|\n| Any subagent status = failed | Send alert to Khuowgn immediately |\n| Any agent stuck > 30 min | Send alert to Khuowgn immediately |\n| Night time 23:00–07:00 UTC+7 | Stay silent unless critical |","newText":"### Every ~10 min — Lead Direct Status Report\n\nSeparate cron (`e7885813`) sends active agent status to Lead's direct chat every 10 minutes.\n\nFormat:\n```\n🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nActive sessions: N\n• [session]: [status] — [task] — [duration]\n```\n\n## 🚨 Always Report Immediately (no silence)\n\n| Condition | Action |\n|---|---|\n| Any subagent status = failed | Send alert to Khuowgn immediately |\n| Any agent stuck > 30 min | Send alert to Khuowgn immediately |\n| Night time 23:00–07:00 UTC+7 | Stay silent unless critical |"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":153,"output":344,"cacheRead":117918,"cacheWrite":591,"totalTokens":119006,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776056141369,"responseId":"062baa4f11f94639894fbb2f72b78403"}}
