       \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 161,\n            \"output\": 402,\n            \"totalTokens\": 35664,\n            \"cacheRead\": 17766,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 17335,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776031328584,\n          \"responseId\": \"062b49618ba3e98360105a7881f89c7c\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"34ae6384\",\n            \"seq\": 14\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:05e6701d-36aa-491c-ab9d-8edd7eeb37f8\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492\",\n      \"label\": \"ahv-qlhv:merge:fe\",\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776002693337,\n      \"sessionId\": \"ad3bea85-2fdb-4f14-99f3-c964588a9b39\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-TroLy\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"status\": \"failed\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776002690782,\n      \"endedAt\": 1776004152498,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 1461716,\n      \"thinkingLevel\": \"medium\",\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-frontend/sessions/ad3bea85-2fdb-4f14-99f3-c964588a9b39.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": []\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:senior-backend:subagent:ce81d04d-cc26-4b7d-82f4-704a8256c73b\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492\",\n      \"label\": \"ahv-qlhv:merge:be\",\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776002693327,\n      \"sessionId\": \"a257979c-3e1e-4845-b903-2fcf80d8a83e\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-TroLy\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"status\": \"failed\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776002690642,\n      \"endedAt\": 1776004152478,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 1461836,\n      \"thinkingLevel\": \"medium\",\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/sessions/a257979c-3e1e-4845-b903-2fcf80d8a83e.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": []\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:prompt-optimizer:telegram:group:-5168104492\",\n      \"kind\": \"group\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"prompt-optimizer_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:-5168104492\",\n        \"accountId\": \"prompt-optimizer_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1775990629434,\n      \"sessionId\": \"731cf84b-b802-4c4a-90b9-2fb6c1177f22\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 20343,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1775990537840,\n      \"endedAt\": 1775990629120,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 91280,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"telegram:-5168104492\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"prompt-optimizer_bot\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/prompt-optimizer/sessions/731cf84b-b802-4c4a-90b9-2fb6c1177f22.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Good, I can see the full ecosystem. No `qlhv` found in memory. Let me now analyze the prompt and produce the optimization output.\\n\\nLet me now run the full Phase 0-5 analysis and produce the output.\\n\\n**Project Detection:**\\n- AGENTS.md exists (confirmed via context)\\n- No package.json detected (empty dir listing - this is a skills workspace, not a code project)\\n- Tech stack: **unknown** — no code files detected in current workspace\\n\\n**Intent Detection:**\\n- Keywords: \\\"đánh giá\\\", \\\"báo cáo\\\", \\\"match database\\\", \\\"logic chưa khớp\\\", \\\"vấn đề\\\"\\n- Category: **Review** + **Research** — a system audit/evaluation task\\n\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"## ⚙️ Prompt Diagnosis\\n\\n### Prompt gốc:\\n> *\\\"master thực hiện triển khai yêu cầu đánh giá, báo cáo cho tôi chi tiết về hệ thống qlhv này xem là có match database với master chưa, có phần logic nào chưa khớp hay có những vấn đề gì\\\"*\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Strengths\\n- ✅ Mục tiêu rõ: đánh giá hệ thống `qlhv` — so khớp DB + logic\\n- ✅ Có yêu cầu báo cáo chi tiết\\n\\n### Issues\\n\\n| Issue | Impact | Suggested Fix |\\n|-------|--------|---------------|\\n| Không chỉ rõ **hệ thống qlhv** nằm ở đâu (repo, đường dẫn, project) | Agent không tìm được codebase → trả lời sai hoặc thừa | Cung cấp repo path hoặc workspace chứa hệ thống qlhv |\\n| Không chỉ rõ **\\\"master\\\"** là ai — là agent `@master-orchestrator`, một repo cụ thể, hay branch/commit? | Routing nhầm → sai agent | Chỉ rõ agent phụ trách hoặc source of truth |\\n| Không có **acceptance criteria** — khi nào thì báo cáo đủ? | Kết quả mở, không biết dừng ở đâu | Thêm tiêu chí đánh giá cụ thể |\\n| Không phân biệt **database nào vs database nào** — so khớp cái gì? | Không rõ scope so sánh | Liệt kê schema cần so sánh (source DB vs target DB) |\\n| Không chỉ rõ **output format** — báo cáo dạng bảng, markdown, issue list? | Không đồng nhất | Chỉ rõ format: markdown / Confluence / file |\\n| Không chỉ rõ **phạm vi logic** — là tầng nào (API, service, repository)? | Kiểm tra lan man hoặc thiếu | Giới hạn: chỉ logic nghiệp vụ + database layer |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Recommended Components\\n\\n| Type | Component | Purpose |\\n|------|-----------|---------|\\n| Orchestrator | `@master-orchestrator` | Điều phối cross-domain review, giao việc cho các agent chuyên biệt |\\n| Skill | `@database-schema-designer` | So khớp schema, phát hiện missing/extra fields, FK constraints |\\n| Skill | `@senior-backend` | Review logic nghiệp vụ, API contracts, service layer |\\n| Skill | `@coding-standards` | Kiểm tra naming, patterns, DRY/KISS compliance |\\n| Skill | `@senior-security` | Phát hiện vấn đề bảo mật trong DB access |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Optimized Prompt — Full Version\\n\\n```\\n## Task: Đánh giá & Báo cáo Hệ thống QLHV — So khớp Database & Logic\\n\\n### 1. Ngữ cảnh\\n- Hệ thống: QLHV (Quản lý Học viên)\\n- Vị trí codebase: <CHỈ_RỜI_ĐƯỜNG_DẪN_REPO_QLHV>  ← THAY BẰNG PATH THỰC TẾ\\n- Database nguồn (source): <TÊN_DB_QLHV>  ← VD: MongoDB collection \\\"students\\\", \\\"courses\\\"\\n- Database master (target): <TÊN_DB_MASTER>  ← VD: MongoDB collection \\\"students\\\", \\\"courses\\\"\\n- Tech stack phát hiện: <AUTO_DETECT_HOẶC_CHỈ_RỖ>\\n\\n### 2. Mục tiêu\\nSo khớp hệ thống QLHV với master, phát hiện:\\n  a) **Database mismatch** — thiếu field, thừa field, sai kiểu dữ liệu, FK orphan\\n  b) **Logic misalignment** — business rules không đồng nhất giữa service layer vs DB\\n  c) **Vấn đề tiềm ẩn** — security holes, missing validations, edge cases chưa xử lý\\n\\n### 3. Workflow thực hiện\\n\\n**Bước 1 — @database-schema-designer**\\n  → Dump schema của cả 2 database (source QLHV + master)\\n  → So sánh field-by-field, type, constraints, indexes\\n  → Output: Bảng diff schema (field mới / thiếu / sai type)\\n\\n**Bước 2 — @senior-backend**\\n  → Review logic nghiệp vụ trong service layer của QLHV\\n  → Kiểm tra API endpoints: request/response contract có match DB schema không\\n  → Output: Danh sách logic chưa khớp hoặc thiếu validation\\n\\n**Bước 3 — @senior-security**\\n  → Kiểm tra truy vấn DB: có SQL/NoSQL injection không?\\n  → Kiểm tra quyền truy cập, auth enforcement\\n  → Output: Danh sách rủi ro bảo mật (nếu có)\\n\\n**Bước 4 — @master-orchestrator**\\n  → Tổng hợp kết quả từ Bước 1–3\\n  → Phân loại: 🔴 Critical / 🟡 Warning / 🟢 OK\\n\\n### 4. Output format (bắt buộc)\\n\\n#### 4.1 Database Diff Table\\n| Schema | Collection/Table | Field | Type (QLHV) | Type (Master) | Status |\\n|--------|-----------------|-------|-------------|---------------|--------|\\n\\n#### 4.2 Logic Issues List\\n| # | Module | Issue | Severity | Recommendation |\\n|---|--------|-------|----------|----------------|\\n\\n#### 4.3 Security Issues List\\n| # | Endpoint/Function | Issue | CVSS-like | Fix |\\n\\n#### 4.4 Summary\\n- Tổng số mismatch: X\\n- Tổng số logic issue: Y\\n- Tổng số security issue: Z\\n- ✅ Có thể proceed hay ❌ Cần fix trước\\n\\n### 5. Ràng buộc\\n- Không sửa code — chỉ đánh giá và báo cáo\\n- Không modify database production\\n- Nếu repo không tìm thấy → báo lỗi ngay và hỏi lại path\\n\\n### 6. Deliverable\\n- Báo cáo hoàn chỉnh dạng Markdown\\n- Đăng lên Confluence page nếu có QLHV workspace\\n\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Optimized Prompt — Quick Version\\n\\n| Intent | Quick Pattern |\\n|--------|--------------|\\n| Review | `@master-orchestrator — đánh giá hệ thống QLHV. So khớp DB + logic vs master. Báo cáo table format: diff schema / logic issues / security. Không sửa, chỉ report.` |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Enhancement Rationale\\n\\n| Enhancement | Reason |\\n|-------------|--------|\\n| Chỉ rõ repo path + collection/table | Agent biết đâu là source để review — tránh hallucinate |\\n| Phân tách Bước 1–3 theo skill chuyên biệt | Đảm bảo mỗi góc nhìn được expert xử lý (DB ≠ logic ≠ security) |\\n| Output table format bắt buộc | Lead nhận được artifact đồng nhất, không phải text tự do |\\n| Phân loại severity (Critical/Warning/OK) | Lead có thể prioritize action ngay |\\n| Không sửa, chỉ report | Đảm bảo agent không tự ý thay đổi production — đúng scope review |\\n\\n---\\n\\n> ⚠️ **Missing Info cần bạn cung cấp thêm:**\\n> 1. **Repo/workspace chứa hệ thống QLHV** nằm ở đâu?\\n> 2. **Tên database + collection/table** cần so khớp là gì?\\n> 3. **Branch/commit master** nào là source of truth?\\n> 4. **Output đích** — gửi ở đâu (Telegram/Confluence/file)?\\n> 5. **Confluence space** có sẵn cho QLHV không?\\n\\nCung cấp thêm thông tin trên → prompt sẵn sàng paste vào agent để thực thi ngay.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 298,\n            \"output\": 2220,\n            \"totalTokens\": 22563,\n            \"cacheRead\": 15219,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 4826,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\nns (e.g., clear bounded contexts, consistent naming, appropriate data typing observed in models, good use of references where appropriate).\\n\\n- CRITICAL ISSUES\\n  - Any showstoppers or major security/data integrity risks (e.g., missing required fields, lack of unique indexes on critical identifiers, no guards against duplicate users, data migration pitfalls).\\n\\n- HIGH ISSUES\\n  - Important concerns that could impact production (e.g., missing compound indexes for high-traffic queries, suboptimal relationship patterns that could cause hot reads, improper use of arrays in heavily updated documents).\\n\\n- MEDIUM ISSUES\\n  - Moderate risks or improvements (e.g., optional fields that should be mandatory for consistency, small normalization opportunities, potential shard-key considerations).\\n\\n- RECOMMENDATIONS\\n  - Concrete, actionable changes grouped by area (schema design, indexing strategy, relationships, data integrity, migrations, operational surveillance, security).\\n\\n- PRIORITY FIX LIST\\n  - A ranked list of fixes with rationale and suggested owners/timeframes.\\n\\n- ADDITIONAL ANALYSIS (optional)\\n  - Compare against Confluence AW space requirements:\\n    - Schema completeness for Confluence specs: chat, khen thuong, bang xep hang, lich su checkin\\n    - Expected conventions for Confluence-related data (namespaces, collections, indexes)\\n  - Scalability probes for large collections:\\n    - attendances, checkins, systemLogs\\n    - Recommendations on sharding strategy, index patterns, TTLs, archival plans\\n\\nWhat I will deliver once I have access:\\n- A complete, well-structured database.md at /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/reviews/database.md with the exact sections and high-quality observations.\\n- Clear evidence-backed findings tied to model files and queries observed in src/modules/*/models/* and src/common/models/*.\\n- If gaps exist in the Confluence-spec coverage, I’ll detail what’s missing and propose concrete schema additions.\\n\\nIf you want me to proceed without providing external access, I can still draft a provisional report template and placeholders, but it will be based on assumptions rather than live code inspection. Let me know which path you prefer, and please share any constraints (e.g., sensitivity, required privilege level, or deadlines).\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-TroLy\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 11995,\n            \"output\": 750,\n            \"totalTokens\": 12745,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1775981830687,\n          \"responseId\": \"DTkIYYQHlv9px8Wyr3gicVbTQrW2S\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"7bda30cd\",\n            \"seq\": 3\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:code-reviewer:subagent:370ec3dd-07f8-4a08-a4d6-823d773bfe5b\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728\",\n      \"label\": \"ahv-works:review:code\",\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-maiychrus25-company-.ltd\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1775982240778,\n      \"sessionId\": \"cfe2ec20-9ce0-407c-a08e-3b1c4cd307ee\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 100807,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"failed\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1775981697335,\n      \"endedAt\": 1775981831284,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 0,\n      \"thinkingLevel\": \"medium\",\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/code-reviewer/sessions/cfe2ec20-9ce0-407c-a08e-3b1c4cd307ee.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": []\n    }\n  ]\n}[... 14016 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"count":23,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:6053576134","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776056232042,"sessionId":"7ae3b683-0b91-4427-abbe-b78ef94eb140","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":130632,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776056083313,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:6053576134","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/7ae3b683-0b91-4427-abbe-b78ef94eb140.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron run shows no entries, which means the cron might not have run yet or the run result isn't recorded yet. The cron might be still running. Let me check the session history of the direct session to see if the report was delivered.Actually, let me reconsider. The cron was enqueued with `runId: manual:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e:1776056112218:2`. It should have run by now. The `runs` showing empty is unusual.\n\nLet me try a different approach - check the sessions to see if there's a new isolated session from this cron."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zvvjgyiavgo1_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":161,"output":160,"totalTokens":119417,"cacheRead":118944,"cacheWrite":152,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776056226800,"responseId":"062baaa4dd9584c442248070774e234c","__openclaw":{"id":"5ef66136","seq":112}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258","kind":"group","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:-5163901258","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776056226292,"sessionId":"8e0cb2bc-8245-4c89-bc2c-e3cca2257d0f","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":85914,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776056225936,"childSessions":["agent:senior-backend:subagent:f42cdd0e-8c76-42e7-ac2a-f1474568e0d4","agent:senior-frontend:subagent:cf1f74df-fd21-47ed-8a91-4c146aead234"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:-5163901258","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/8e0cb2bc-8245-4c89-bc2c-e3cca2257d0f.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"